<h2 style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;text-align: center;background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</h2><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px">一、</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">考前准备及注意事项</span></strong></p><p style=";text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">（一）</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">考前准备</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">1.准备好身份证、准考证放置考试桌面备查。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">2.准备好带摄像功能的手机1部，用于线上答题。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">3.保证以上设备电量充足（最好接通电源），建议全程使用外接电源或接入移动电源。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">4.手机安装“超星学习通APP”（</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">按照附件1提示下载</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">）；确保超星学习通APP摄像头正常使用。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">5.将手机设置</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #0000ff;font-size: 16px">免打扰模式</span></strong><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">（按照附件2要求操作），</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">进入考试系统前，须</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">将手机</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">上与考试无关网页</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">及</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">应用程序</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">退出登录（按照附件2要求操作）</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">，避免由于程序冲突影响考试软件运行。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">6.须选择环境安静、采光良好、网络信号好的室内进行考试，注意光线要柔和，不选择强光，不逆光。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">（二）考试注意事项</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">1.答题时点击“下一题”按钮，以保存上一题答题记录，避免失误、防止数据丢失。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">2.系统支持拍照上传功能，如遇主观题或计算题，可拍摄清晰的答题页上传系统，并将书写纸保存15日。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">3.手写主观题时，手机摆放要求前置摄像头能拍到考生的头部、手部及书写纸。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">4.考试过程中，如考试手机遇突发事件（如死机、黑屏等），请十分钟内联系学校说明情况，并及时重新进入考试界面。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">5.开始答题后，截屏、分屏、多任务开启等非答题操作都会造成考试系统的异常退出。由于考生异常退出考试系统导致考试时间损失或无法完成考试的，考生须自行承担责任。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">6.使用小米手机的同学需在进入考试平台前做好以下设置：</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">点击手机【设置】--搜索【锁屏画报】--将【开启画报】打开--【重启手机】。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">7.考试环境桌面清理。桌面要保持整洁，除手写主观题、计算题时使用的空白书写纸，不得放置其他与考试相关的纸质资料。一经发现，将按考试作弊处理。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">8.身份核对。开考前学习通会进行人脸匹配，匹配异常者不得参加考试。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">9.对于考试现场发现或者事后有证据举报的违纪、作弊等情况，学校将查阅抓拍图片。若发现举报属实，将按照相关规定严肃处理。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">10.进入考试前，学习通会在考试通知中发布考生须知，考生须认真阅读后点击确认，进入考试。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">11.其他未尽事宜，以学校通知为准。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px">二、</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">模拟测试</span></strong></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">测试时间：2022年3月18日14:30—17:30</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">测试平台：超星学习通</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">三、正式线上考试</span></strong></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">1.考试时间：2022年3月20日9:00～12:00</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">2.考试方式：手机登录“超星考试客户端”（超星学习通APP）进行线上考试。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">3.考试科目：文化素质+职业技能测试。满分为450分，考试时长为180分钟。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">4.登录时间：3月20日上午8:30～9:00，考生提前登录超星考试客户端（超星学习通APP）确认考试信息。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">5.迟到30分钟不能进入考场考试，开考90分钟内不得交卷。考试期间，请保持网络畅通，否则后果自负。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 7px;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 7px;text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px;background: #ffffff"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">四</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">、线上考试违纪处理</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 27px;text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px;background: #ffffff"><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">考生应按照</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">考试</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">要求，自觉接受考风考纪监督，凡违反纪律要求的，考试成绩记为0分，同时按国家相关文件处理。考试期间，有如下行为视为考试违纪：</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">1.考试房间出现除考生以外的其他人；</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">2.考试桌面出现与考试无关的物品；</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">3.考试期间不得离开座位；</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">4.与他人联系；</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">5.将试卷或其它有关考试内容传出考场；</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">6.请他人代考；</span></p><p style="text-indent: 382px;text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px;background: #ffffff"><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent: 382px;text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px;background: #ffffff"><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent: 430px;text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 33px;background: #ffffff"><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">特此通知</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 24px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 24px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 24px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 24px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px">附件<span style="font-family: Calibri">1</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 24px">江西软件职业技术大学</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 24px">202</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 24px"><span style="font-family: Calibri">2</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 24px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">年</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 24px">高职单招</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 24px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">线上考试系统</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 24px">学生</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 24px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">使用手册</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 27px"><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-weight: bold;font-size: 19px">一、</span><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">安装登录</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;line-height: 27px"><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-weight: bold;font-size: 19px">1.</span><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">安装</span></span></strong></p><p style=";text-indent: 37px;line-height: 27px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">江西软件职业技术大学线上考试系统支持Android和IOS两大移动操作系统</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">，可通过以下两种方式下载安装。</span></p><p style=";text-indent: 19px;line-height: 27px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">①应用市场搜索“</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #0000ff;font-size: 19px">学习通</span></strong><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">”，查找到图标为</span><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2022-03-17%2011%3A16%3A558e2475c5811772653855e524ce35cd6.png?Expires=1962847015&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=r0Ot%2B%2FYRych291mdp7GtSFlEKw4%3D" width="45" height="50"/><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">的App，下载并安装。</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-ideograph;line-height: 27px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;②扫描下面的二维码，跳转到对应链接下载App并安装（如用微信扫描二维码请选择在浏览器打开）。</span></p><p style=";text-align: center"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2022-03-17%2011%3A17%3A031c383245b3c7899708cc8dce941e3f2.png?Expires=1962847023&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=nwRvX7yHSJXUkB%2FaGHVwu8W4CEQ%3D" width="367" height="337"/><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=";text-indent: 37px;line-height: 27px"><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">注意：Android系统用户通过以上两种方式下载安装时若提示“未知应用来源”，请确认继续安装；IOS系统用户安装时需要动态验证，按照系统提示进行操作即可。</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">（注意：请确保</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;color: #c00000;font-size: 19px">学习通APP版本为</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;color: #c00000;font-size: 19px">5</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;color: #c00000;font-size: 19px">.</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;color: #c00000;font-size: 19px">1</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;color: #c00000;font-size: 19px">.</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;color: #c00000;font-size: 19px">0</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">）</span></p><p style="text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-ideograph;line-height: 27px"><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-weight: bold;font-size: 19px">2.</span><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">登录学习通</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">（这一步特别注意：</span></span><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;color: #c00000;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">千万不要</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">点击</span>“<span style="font-family: 宋体">新用户注册</span>”<span style="font-family: 宋体">或</span>“<span style="font-family: 宋体">手机验证码登录</span>”<span style="font-family: 宋体">，直接点击最下方</span>“<span style="font-family: 宋体">其他登录方式</span>”<span style="font-family: 宋体">。若因此步骤操作有误导致无法收到考试通知，</span></span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">考生自行负责</span><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">）</span></span></p><p style="margin-right: 0;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 37px;text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-ideograph;line-height: 27px"><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">（</span>1<span style="font-family: 宋体">）选择</span>“</span><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;color: #0000ff;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">其他登录方式</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px">”<span style="font-family: 宋体">，依次输入</span>“</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;color: #0000ff;font-size: 19px">江西软件职业技术大学</span><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px">”<span style="font-family: 宋体">、</span></span><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px">“</span><span style=";font-family: Calibri;color: #0000ff;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">考生号</span></span><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px">”<span style="font-family: 宋体">、</span>“</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;color: #0000ff;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: Calibri">jx</span>身份证</span><span style=";font-family: Calibri;color: #0000ff;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">后六位</span></span><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px">”</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">（</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">如<span style="font-family: Calibri">jx123456</span></span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">）</span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">，</span><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">点击登录。（备注：</span></span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: Calibri">jx</span>为江西缩写，</span><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">若身份证后六位中出现字母</span></span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: Calibri">X</span></span><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">，一律输入</span></span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">大</span><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">写</span></span><span style=";font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: Calibri">X</span></span><span style=";font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">即可）</span></span></p><p style=";text-align: center"><span style="position: absolute;z-index: 1;left: 0px;margin-left: 428.1333px;margin-top: 70.9333px;width: 132.0000px;height: 26.0000px"><br/></span><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2022-03-17%2011%3A17%3A45a1e9741a2be17d514149362615d16a3.png?Expires=1962847065&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signatu